==Gagauz==

===Etymology===
Apparently combines the Turkic root ''Bash(i)'' 'head' and the (originally Mongol) polyvalent title ''[[Khan]]''

===Noun===
'''Bashkan''' (''plural'' '''[[Bashkans]]''')

# Title of the [[governor]] of the Gagauz-Yeri Autonomous Region (since 19 June 1995) within independent Moldova.

